title: Productivity Workshop On Next Month (Government of Barbados - Office of the Prime Minister)
text: ( Source : Government of Barbados - Office of the Prime Minister ) ( Productivity Council ) The Productivity Council will host a free half-day workshop - Lean Applications to Improve Productivity - on Thursday, November 5 , at Accra Beach Hotel
